		<div class="comment-author vcard">
			<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/7f38d517927bb4a8a8d52b4f164ea0c5?s=48&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />
