		<div class="comment-body"><p>bee stings cause me mild allergic reactions &#8211; not epipen serious but worst than most people.  Meat tenderizer dissolves proteins and helps reduce the swelling / neutralize the venom.  I purchased some essential oils and the Purification oil and lavender worked great.  I just returned from a two week bicycle tour where I got a bee logged under a helmet strap.  Calmly stopped and applied the meat tenderizer and then the oils.  I forgot I had gotten stung &#8211; it worked great.</p>
<p>Thanks for the show.</p>
</div>

